column2: URL to access web interface of Jenkins server.

[{u'ToPort': u'22', u'IpProtocol': u'tcp', u'CidrIp': u'0.0.0.0/0', u'FromPort': u'22'}, {u'ToPort': u'8080', u'IpProtocol': u'tcp', u'CidrIp': u'0.0.0.0/0', u'FromPort': u'8080'}, {u'ToPort': u'-1', u'IpProtocol': u'icmp', u'CidrIp': u'0.0.0.0/0', u'FromPort': u'-1'}]

{u'Fn::Base64': {u'Fn::Join': [u'', [u'#!/bin/bash -ex
', u'aws configure set default.region ', {u'Ref': u'AWS::Region'}, u'
', u'INSTANCE_ID=`curl -s http://169.254.169.254/latest/meta-data/instance-id`
', u'aws ec2 associate-address --instance-id $INSTANCE_ID --allocation-id ', {u'Fn::GetAtt': [u'ElasticIP', u'AllocationId']}, u'
', u'wget http://pkg.jenkins-ci.org/redhat/jenkins-1.616-1.1.noarch.rpm
', u'rpm --install jenkins-1.616-1.1.noarch.rpm
', u'sed -i -e 's/JENKINS_ARGS=\"\"/JENKINS_ARGS=\"--argumentsRealm.passwd.admin=', {u'Ref': u'JenkinsAdminPassword'}, u' --argumentsRealm.roles.admin=admin\"/g' /etc/sysconfig/jenkins
', u'echo "<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?><hudson><version>1.0</version><useSecurity>true</useSecurity><authorizationStrategy class=\"hudson.security.FullControlOnceLoggedInAuthorizationStrategy\"/><securityRealm class=\"hudson.security.LegacySecurityRealm\"/></hudson>" > /var/lib/jenkins/config.xml
', u'service jenkins start
']]}}
